\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Mission\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Missionary_Society\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Missionary_Society\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"16th January,1902\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"North China\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"the son\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"missionaries\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around the age of six he was sent to the UK to boarding school and subsequently attended Edinburgh University where he gained a reputation as the fastest man in Scotland.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999529277386, \"rank\": 4.628176626302705e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 858, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Edinburgh\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 3.751343756993535e-11, \"text\": \"Edinburgh University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Edinburgh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Edinburgh\"}, {\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5463118723766393, \"rank\": 0.8303840080629984, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"a reputation\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest man\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His speed also led him to represent Scotland at rugby.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5463118723766393, \"rank\": 0.8303840080629984, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His speed\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He played seven times and scored tries in four successive matches.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tries\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"four successive matches\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eric Liddell with his brother Rob at Eltham College in June 1908.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0206371029304016e-75, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}, {\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eltham_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0551735883207565e-37, \"text\": \"Eltham College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eltham_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eltham_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his brother\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"Rob\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/The Eric Liddell Community Selected to participate the in the 1924 Olympics, Liddell would have been among the favorites for the showcase 100 meter dash.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"score\": 0.9999527069181952, \"rank\": 4.6431039523126616e-05, \"text\": \"Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eric Liddell Community\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1924 Olympics\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"the favorites\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"the showcase 100 meter dash\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, as a devout Christian, he dropped out of the event because the qualifying heats were scheduled for a Sunday.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9930674637112872, \"rank\": 0.00698092750403588, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying heats\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"a Sunday\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, he switched to the 200 and 400-meter sprints.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 200 and 400-meter sprints\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Games, despite being drawn in the challenging outside line against a powerful field, he triumphed in the 400-meters in an Olympic and World Record time of 47.6 seconds.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenging outside line\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful field\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400-meters\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic and World Record time\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"47.6 seconds\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also claimed a bronze medal in the 200 meters.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 meters\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LIDDELL AND CHINA After the Olympics, Liddell turned down the opportunity of a sporting career in the UK and returned to China to pursue his parents' vocation as a missionary.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"score\": 0.9999527069181952, \"rank\": 4.6431039523126616e-05, \"text\": \"Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\"}, {\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999529277386, \"rank\": 4.628176626302705e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999781180124, \"rank\": 8.81438326248945e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting career\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"his parents' vocation\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"a missionary\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His first job was as a teacher at an Anglo-Chinese College where he used his athletic experience to train boys in a number of different sports.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ying_Wa_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anglo-Chinese College\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ying_Wa_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ying_Wa_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His first job\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"a teacher\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"his athletic experience\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He set up football, basketball, softball, baseball, ping pong, tennis and volleyball teams in Tianjin.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tianjin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.113591950803339e-21, \"text\": \"Tianjin\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tianjin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tianjin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"softball\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"baseball\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"ping pong\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis and volleyball teams\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\"